<div id="about-me" class="about contrast-bg">
  <h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
  <hr style="width:40%">
  <div class="aboutme-grid">
    <div class="presentation">
      <%= image_tag "profile.JPG", class: 'Profile pic' %>
      <p>I'm a <strong>Full Stack Web Developer</strong> with a background in the teaching industry. Living in Japan for 3 years, I have taken an interest in the lifestyle of the people here and how similar and yet different it is from my hometown in Spain.
        <br>
        <br>
        I believe technology has so much more to <strong>give to the community</strong>, be it by bringing people together or by revitalizing isolated communities, and I would love to be part of it!
        <br>
        <br>
        I also have interest in Data Science and Applied Machine Learning to solve Real-World problems, so... please don't get too confused if you see some ML / AI project mixed in!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-stack">
      <h2>MY TECH STACK</h2>
      <hr style="width:20%">
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="front-back-others">
